1
00:00:19,690 --> 00:00:26,890
♪Lights of swords are like
a splash of rivers♪

2
00:00:27,280 --> 00:00:34,320
♪Shadows of swords cover the seasons♪

3
00:00:34,700 --> 00:00:38,090
♪The clear water cuts off the gorge♪

4
00:00:38,910 --> 00:00:42,190
♪Which is facing the armed army♪

5
00:00:42,410 --> 00:00:45,780
♪Missing a pot of cold wine♪

6
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:49,590
♪Drunk in the middle of sand♪

7
00:00:49,670 --> 00:00:53,520
♪The place of peace of mind
is my hometown♪

8
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:57,240
♪But my hometown is by your side♪

9
00:00:57,240 --> 00:01:01,520
♪Who forgets about the grudges
in the past♪

10
00:01:01,830 --> 00:01:04,920
♪Don’t blame the west wind
for your tears♪

11
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:08,700
♪To meet and to part are like a dream♪

12
00:01:09,430 --> 00:01:12,610
♪Well-armed with armor and weapons♪

13
00:01:12,610 --> 00:01:16,960
♪Where the surging river is going♪

14
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:22,960
♪Together we go to the end of the world♪

15
00:01:24,380 --> 00:01:29,980
=Legend of Fei=

16
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:32,940
=Episode 15=

17
00:01:34,230 --> 00:01:37,630
He is the descendant of
the famous North Blade.

18
00:01:37,630 --> 00:01:39,830
He vanished from sight many years ago.

19
00:01:39,830 --> 00:01:41,630
Now he is still alive and kicking.

20
00:01:41,630 --> 00:01:43,400
From what I know of him,

21
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:45,800
he can do whatever it takes to survive.

22
00:01:45,800 --> 00:01:48,160
Is that right, Master Ji?

23
00:01:52,360 --> 00:01:54,290
I’ve met tons of perfidious people.

24
00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:57,280
But after I met Mr. Yin,

25
00:01:58,480 --> 00:02:00,870
I realized that not
all ingrates lack humanity.

26
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:04,750
I agree with what Mr. Xie just said.

27
00:02:05,510 --> 00:02:07,680
That old demon stole my stuff.

28
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:09,440
He is a thief!

29
00:02:09,440 --> 00:02:10,800
Whether it’s the Mountain Sword

30
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:12,960
or any other things,
they all belong to the Yin family.

31
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:14,190
I just got my stuff back.

32
00:02:14,190 --> 00:02:15,630
Isn’t that a rightful thing to do?

33
00:02:15,630 --> 00:02:16,910
Since it’s a rightful thing to do,

34
00:02:16,910 --> 00:02:18,240
why would I tell you strangers

35
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,670
about it?

36
00:02:20,670 --> 00:02:22,520
To recruit another group of thieves?

37
00:02:24,670 --> 00:02:25,720
All right.

38
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:27,630
Mr. Yin, you’d better know
what you are doing.

39
00:02:32,550 --> 00:02:33,360
What are you looking at?

40
00:02:33,370 --> 00:02:33,860
Get out!

41
00:02:58,160 --> 00:02:58,880
You…!

42
00:02:59,390 --> 00:03:00,480
Why are you out again?

43
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:03,000
I’m tired of being inside.

44
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,720
I can’t stay here forever.

45
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:07,360
Do you want to carry the blade

46
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:09,470
and confront with
the Dragon Master again?

47
00:03:09,470 --> 00:03:11,670
I’m self-aware.

48
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,750
That’s good.

49
00:03:14,750 --> 00:03:15,390
All right.

50
00:03:15,390 --> 00:03:17,160
I’ll go out to check the situation.

51
00:03:18,190 --> 00:03:19,470
I’ll go with you.

52
00:03:20,110 --> 00:03:22,110
My footwork is good, and I can run fast.

53
00:03:22,110 --> 00:03:23,080
How about you?

54
00:03:23,470 --> 00:03:25,470
You are skilled in martial arts?
Do you want to fight again?

55
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:35,720
All right, just go back.

56
00:03:40,030 --> 00:03:41,750
Let... Let me go!

57
00:03:48,030 --> 00:03:49,080
Chuchu.

58
00:03:51,030 --> 00:03:53,170
Didn’t Mr. Xie come back with you?

59
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:56,270
He went to check things out.

60
00:03:56,270 --> 00:03:58,960
We can’t just sit here and do nothing.

61
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:01,270
His footwork is so well.

62
00:04:01,270 --> 00:04:02,800
He should be fine.

63
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:05,910
That guy is good-for-nothing.

64
00:04:09,270 --> 00:04:11,030
Strangely speaking,

65
00:04:12,830 --> 00:04:14,240
if a person’s footwork

66
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:16,390
reaches to a certain level,

67
00:04:16,390 --> 00:04:18,830
he might not be good at martial arts,

68
00:04:18,830 --> 00:04:20,770
but he shouldn’t know nothing about it.

69
00:04:22,790 --> 00:04:24,110
That’s true.

70
00:04:24,110 --> 00:04:26,500
I never saw him use any moves.

71
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,600
If a person

72
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:30,920
has no experience in fighting

73
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:33,880
and can’t predict the next move
of the opponent,

74
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:37,320
even he runs as fast as the wind,

75
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:39,070
he can’t be as flexible as Mr. Xie

76
00:04:39,070 --> 00:04:40,990
just by running around

77
00:04:41,670 --> 00:04:43,980
and dodging.

78
00:04:46,350 --> 00:04:49,220
But I only saw him run.

79
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:51,710
Then why?

80
00:04:53,230 --> 00:04:54,550
I don’t know.

81
00:04:54,550 --> 00:04:57,320
I don’t think he will tell me
even I ask him.

82
00:04:57,320 --> 00:05:00,200
Mr. Xie is a mysterious person.

83
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,110
Yeah.

84
00:05:03,110 --> 00:05:04,850
And he is full of lies.

85
00:05:11,510 --> 00:05:12,470
What are you drawing?

86
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,720
Take a look.

87
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:23,880
This is…

88
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:26,640
Duan Jiuniang’s Yellow and Green Palm?

89
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:29,350
You recognize it?

90
00:05:29,350 --> 00:05:31,390
I’m afraid I didn’t draw it well.

91
00:05:31,390 --> 00:05:33,200
Why do you draw that?

92
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:34,550
No.

93
00:05:34,550 --> 00:05:36,640
How do you remember these moves?

94
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:40,070
I had a good memory when I was young.

95
00:05:40,070 --> 00:05:41,670
I see a thing once
and I can remember it.

96
00:05:41,670 --> 00:05:42,440
Back then,

97
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:45,040
I saw you and Duan Jiuniang
joust in the courtyard,

98
00:05:45,070 --> 00:05:47,160
and I memorized it.

99
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:49,000
During these days,

100
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:51,140
I heard a lot of old stories.

101
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:54,770
Especially what Yin Pei said.

102
00:05:55,390 --> 00:05:56,320
I think

103
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:58,720
it’s a pity if no one

104
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:00,020
keeps practicing this martial art.

105
00:06:00,950 --> 00:06:02,930
So you want to record it?

106
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,550
I’m trying to recall

107
00:06:06,550 --> 00:06:08,040
as much as I can.

108
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:10,640
Maybe there will be martial arts genius

109
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:12,550
who can get some inspiration

110
00:06:12,550 --> 00:06:13,670
from these records

111
00:06:13,670 --> 00:06:15,760
and carry on these martial arts.

112
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:21,550
Recording it in a book
can make it last forever

113
00:06:21,550 --> 00:06:22,910
and be learned by posterity.

114
00:06:23,950 --> 00:06:25,040
Chuchu.

115
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:27,270
Your idea is excellent.

116
00:06:28,230 --> 00:06:30,690
Actually, I didn’t think that much.

117
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,070
It’s a pity.

118
00:06:33,070 --> 00:06:34,390
That’s all I can do

119
00:06:34,390 --> 00:06:35,890
on my own.

120
00:06:36,830 --> 00:06:37,880
I’m afraid

121
00:06:39,070 --> 00:06:42,640
Duan Jiuniang’s Yellow and Green Palm
will be lost one day.

122
00:06:44,320 --> 00:06:45,790
My understanding of
Yellow and Green Palm

123
00:06:45,790 --> 00:06:47,330
is quite shallow.

124
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:48,950
But,

125
00:06:48,950 --> 00:06:50,980
I have the Yellow and Green Spirit
in my body.

126
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:53,110
Now you recorded it,

127
00:06:53,110 --> 00:06:55,160
which means Duan Jiuniang’s
Yellow and Green Palm

128
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:56,990
is not completely lost yet.

129
00:06:59,510 --> 00:07:00,820
I’m just afraid

130
00:07:01,230 --> 00:07:02,520
I can’t practice it well

131
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:04,790
and humiliate myself.

132
00:07:05,790 --> 00:07:06,830
Fei.

133
00:07:06,830 --> 00:07:08,230
You can’t think that way.

134
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:11,550
Duan Jiuniang passed the Yellow and
Green Palm to you in person,

135
00:07:11,550 --> 00:07:12,720
which means she recognized you

136
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:14,230
and liked you.

137
00:07:14,230 --> 00:07:15,070
Besides,

138
00:07:15,070 --> 00:07:18,230
you have fought against those masters,

139
00:07:18,230 --> 00:07:19,370
and you were doing great.

140
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:00,200
Where are they?

141
00:08:00,200 --> 00:08:01,510
My lord.

142
00:08:01,510 --> 00:08:02,550
We have searched the whole mountain.

143
00:08:02,550 --> 00:08:03,960
There is no trace of them.

144
00:08:10,350 --> 00:08:11,920
This is the foot of Mount Heng.

145
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,690
They must be hiding
in the secret tunnel.

146
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:16,740
Pass on my order.

147
00:08:17,350 --> 00:08:18,760
Let’s head to the site of
Mount Heng Sect!

148
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:19,440
Yes!

149
00:08:33,230 --> 00:08:34,440
Mr. Yin.

150
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,710
You should be hungry now.

151
00:08:35,710 --> 00:08:37,120
Do you want some fruit?

152
00:08:38,470 --> 00:08:39,700
Why are you being so nice to me?

153
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:43,670
You didn’t eat much all the way here.

154
00:08:43,670 --> 00:08:44,940
I’m afraid you will be feeble.

155
00:08:45,590 --> 00:08:46,910
Don’t worry.

156
00:08:46,910 --> 00:08:48,440
It has no poison.

157
00:08:53,880 --> 00:08:54,770
I won’t eat.

158
00:08:57,470 --> 00:08:58,600
I’m dying anyway.

159
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:00,720
What does it matter
whether I eat it or not?

160
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:08,350
Wait.

161
00:09:10,350 --> 00:09:11,320
What’s wrong?

162
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,110
You...

163
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,210
Do you know how to unlock the acupoint?

164
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:24,000
You can leave.

165
00:09:51,030 --> 00:09:52,080
Did you hear anything?

166
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:53,200
It should be the wind.

167
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:55,280
No one can move that fast.

168
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:02,150
My lord.

169
00:10:02,150 --> 00:10:03,590
We didn’t find them.

170
00:10:06,110 --> 00:10:08,790
You’ve been searching all day
and got nothing?

171
00:10:08,790 --> 00:10:10,280
Useless waste!

172
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:14,030
Fei.

173
00:10:17,230 --> 00:10:18,710
How is your investigation going?

174
00:10:18,710 --> 00:10:20,350
This secret tunnel extends
in all directions.

175
00:10:20,350 --> 00:10:21,840
There are many traps

176
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:24,400
and many intersections.

177
00:10:25,150 --> 00:10:26,230
We are underground now.

178
00:10:26,230 --> 00:10:28,200
It’s already hard to tell the direction.

179
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,520
What’s worse,

180
00:10:29,520 --> 00:10:30,640
we don’t have a map.

181
00:10:30,640 --> 00:10:32,070
It’s easy to get stuck here.

182
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,710
What should we do?

183
00:10:35,710 --> 00:10:37,880
I don’t want to stay
in this cave forever.

184
00:10:39,280 --> 00:10:40,350
There is nothing we can do.

185
00:10:40,350 --> 00:10:42,430
We can only hide in here now.

186
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:46,080
Hope they will leave soon.

187
00:10:47,280 --> 00:10:48,120
Miss Zhou.

188
00:10:52,910 --> 00:10:53,840
Miss Zhou.

189
00:10:54,790 --> 00:10:57,150
I heard that those who practice
Snow-breaking Blade

190
00:10:57,150 --> 00:10:58,500
are often late bloomers.

191
00:10:59,400 --> 00:11:00,170
But,

192
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:03,200
I noticed that your broadsword play
is quite well now.

193
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:04,530
Did you start to practice it
when you were young?

194
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:08,640
How long have you been practicing it?

195
00:11:12,150 --> 00:11:14,620
When I left home, my mother…

196
00:11:17,790 --> 00:11:20,840
Mother told me not to
give out my information easily.

197
00:11:21,110 --> 00:11:22,880
I didn’t learn it when I was young.

198
00:11:23,350 --> 00:11:25,200
I have practiced it for about
two or three years.

199
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,710
Two or three years?

200
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:29,350
Is that too long?

201
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,520
One or two years.

202
00:11:34,520 --> 00:11:35,500
Anyway, that’s it.

203
00:11:39,710 --> 00:11:42,030
Unless you cut corners
and practice an evil Kungfu,

204
00:11:42,030 --> 00:11:43,670
otherwise, it takes decades of efforts

205
00:11:43,670 --> 00:11:46,110
to master a Kungfu.

206
00:11:46,110 --> 00:11:47,260
You are making progress

207
00:11:47,760 --> 00:11:49,290
at a really fast speed.

208
00:11:49,670 --> 00:11:50,710
Come on.

209
00:11:50,710 --> 00:11:51,960
I know myself.

210
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,150
With my ability,

211
00:11:53,150 --> 00:11:55,840
I’m just humiliating my family.

212
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:56,830
Fei,

213
00:11:57,280 --> 00:11:58,510
how long have you been practicing it?

214
00:11:59,470 --> 00:12:00,500
More than half a year.

215
00:12:06,590 --> 00:12:08,150
I have Yellow and Green Spirit
in my body.

216
00:12:08,150 --> 00:12:09,520
I feel

217
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:12,400
it’s infiltrating every move
of Snow-breaking Blade.

218
00:12:13,280 --> 00:12:14,110
Yeah.

219
00:12:14,110 --> 00:12:15,850
We’ve been at death’s door
several times.

220
00:12:16,760 --> 00:12:18,440
Our fearless Master Zhou

221
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:20,470
was also honed by masters
of different schools.

222
00:12:20,470 --> 00:12:21,880
It’s also a rare opportunity.

223
00:12:23,590 --> 00:12:24,740
You eavesdropped on me.

224
00:12:26,790 --> 00:12:27,790
What are you doing?

225
00:12:32,880 --> 00:12:34,590
The younger generation is awesome.

226
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:41,550
My lord, the entrance is over there.

227
00:12:47,280 --> 00:12:49,320
You can’t escape this time.

228
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:05,590
Back then,

229
00:13:05,590 --> 00:13:07,590
when the Mount Heng Sect escaped,

230
00:13:07,590 --> 00:13:09,230
the entrance of the secret tunnel
was deliberately unsealed

231
00:13:09,230 --> 00:13:11,320
to delay the pursuers.

232
00:13:11,320 --> 00:13:13,470
Without someone who knows
the tunnel well leading for them,

233
00:13:13,470 --> 00:13:14,960
they won’t be able to find us

234
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:16,590
in a while.

235
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:20,080
I think they are hitting the gong

236
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:22,200
to scare us.

237
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:24,400
Don’t panic.

238
00:13:26,110 --> 00:13:27,230
Yeah.

239
00:13:28,150 --> 00:13:29,520
It’s like that

240
00:13:29,520 --> 00:13:30,780
when I was checking the surroundings.

241
00:13:31,280 --> 00:13:33,670
If I hadn’t memorized the way back,

242
00:13:33,670 --> 00:13:35,590
it would be difficult to
come back from outside.

243
00:13:36,790 --> 00:13:38,960
It’s easy for that old guy to come in
but hard to leave.

244
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:40,280
We don’t know

245
00:13:40,280 --> 00:13:41,460
who will die here today.

246
00:13:41,760 --> 00:13:43,280
They can just sneak in

247
00:13:43,280 --> 00:13:44,790
and attack us.

248
00:13:45,230 --> 00:13:46,820
Why are they hitting the gong?

249
00:13:50,110 --> 00:13:52,280
I’ve been treating you well!

250
00:13:52,320 --> 00:13:55,030
Gold and jewelry, silk and satin.

251
00:13:55,030 --> 00:13:56,710
Have I ever been stingy about it?

252
00:13:56,710 --> 00:13:59,320
I don’t care whether you are
greedy for money or women,

253
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:02,670
I’ve given you whatever you want!

254
00:14:02,670 --> 00:14:04,880
Why did you take an empty scabbard?

255
00:14:04,880 --> 00:14:08,400
The Mountain Sword is
broken into pieces. It’s worthless.

256
00:14:08,400 --> 00:14:09,910
Just bring it back to me.

257
00:14:09,910 --> 00:14:12,790
I won’t punish you, all right?

258
00:14:12,790 --> 00:14:14,710
It seems that Dragon Master
won’t give up

259
00:14:14,710 --> 00:14:16,320
catching you.

260
00:14:20,520 --> 00:14:22,320
Twenty years ago,

261
00:14:22,320 --> 00:14:25,080
he hurt tons of people

262
00:14:25,080 --> 00:14:27,000
to get my father’s treasure.

263
00:14:29,470 --> 00:14:30,640
Now,

264
00:14:30,640 --> 00:14:32,760
I have this treasure.

265
00:14:32,760 --> 00:14:35,670
And it was stolen by his own dog.

266
00:14:35,670 --> 00:14:36,640
Tell me,

267
00:14:36,640 --> 00:14:38,470
how can he feel good about it?

268
00:14:40,110 --> 00:14:42,150
You piece of crap,

269
00:14:42,150 --> 00:14:44,420
do you have anything to do
with the Yin family?

270
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:50,780
There is no need to hide.

271
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:52,590
The Yin family

272
00:14:52,590 --> 00:14:55,230
was wiped out by my brothers
a long time ago.

273
00:14:55,230 --> 00:14:56,350
With your age,

274
00:14:56,350 --> 00:14:58,840
you might just be
an insignificant bastard!

275
00:14:59,660 --> 00:15:02,210
I hate people calling me
bastard the most.

276
00:15:15,550 --> 00:15:16,470
Not good.

277
00:15:17,080 --> 00:15:18,790
I seem to hear that

278
00:15:18,790 --> 00:15:20,790
the Dragon Master
has a team of blind people

279
00:15:20,790 --> 00:15:22,230
hit the gong.

280
00:15:22,230 --> 00:15:23,350
They can know what’s ahead in the dark

281
00:15:23,350 --> 00:15:24,710
based on the echo

282
00:15:24,710 --> 00:15:25,970
of the gong.

283
00:15:26,520 --> 00:15:28,350
If so,

284
00:15:28,350 --> 00:15:30,450
they can get back

285
00:15:31,080 --> 00:15:32,890
without the need to

286
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:34,870
explore the alleys
and traps by themselves.

287
00:15:35,670 --> 00:15:36,880
I’m afraid this secret tunnel

288
00:15:37,470 --> 00:15:38,640
won’t be able to trap them for too long.

289
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:43,320
Master Ji,

290
00:15:43,320 --> 00:15:44,960
if so,

291
00:15:44,960 --> 00:15:46,670
how long will they find us?

292
00:15:47,590 --> 00:15:49,030
It’s hard to say.

293
00:15:49,030 --> 00:15:51,040
If it’s as you said,

294
00:15:51,760 --> 00:15:53,600
I’m afraid they will be here soon.

295
00:16:01,400 --> 00:16:02,640
Where are you going?

296
00:16:03,640 --> 00:16:05,110
I’m going to check the outside.

297
00:16:05,110 --> 00:16:06,710
If it’s safe outside,

298
00:16:06,710 --> 00:16:08,130
we should get out first.

299
00:16:10,440 --> 00:16:11,200
Don’t worry.

300
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:12,520
I can even explore
the Fortress of the Forty-Eight.

301
00:16:12,520 --> 00:16:14,030
This tunnel of Mount Heng
is just a piece of cake.

302
00:16:19,110 --> 00:16:20,520
Stay here and wait for me.

303
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:30,000
Why are you always running outside?

304
00:16:47,880 --> 00:16:49,000
Miss Zhou.

305
00:16:52,150 --> 00:16:53,840
Can you do me a favor?

306
00:16:54,880 --> 00:16:55,760
Go ahead.

307
00:16:59,110 --> 00:17:00,550
Dragon Master

308
00:17:02,470 --> 00:17:03,840
should be killed.

309
00:17:08,680 --> 00:17:10,020
Who are you?

310
00:17:10,710 --> 00:17:12,400
What kind of hero

311
00:17:12,400 --> 00:17:13,920
are you to just dodge?

312
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:22,000
Keep moving.

313
00:17:29,760 --> 00:17:31,560
If anyone else

314
00:17:31,560 --> 00:17:33,430
teaches a girl like you,

315
00:17:33,430 --> 00:17:34,760
they will make you learn

316
00:17:34,760 --> 00:17:36,230
the labor-saving and light weapons

317
00:17:36,230 --> 00:17:38,560
like dart and whip.

318
00:17:39,110 --> 00:17:40,190
Otherwise,

319
00:17:40,190 --> 00:17:41,350
they will let you master

320
00:17:41,350 --> 00:17:43,590
a hidden weapon.

321
00:17:43,590 --> 00:17:45,070
It’s enough to save your life

322
00:17:45,070 --> 00:17:46,680
as long as your footwork is not bad.

323
00:17:47,350 --> 00:17:48,350
I don’t know

324
00:17:48,350 --> 00:17:50,000
why your elders

325
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:51,710
made you use a blade

326
00:17:51,710 --> 00:17:53,900
and taught you the Snow-breaking Blade.

327
00:17:54,680 --> 00:17:55,590
Yes.

328
00:17:56,520 --> 00:17:57,350
More than one person

329
00:17:57,350 --> 00:17:59,310
told me that my bones
are not strong enough.

330
00:17:59,310 --> 00:18:00,920
It takes twice the effort
to practice the blade.

331
00:18:02,920 --> 00:18:04,110
So?

332
00:18:05,350 --> 00:18:07,170
Did anyone tell you that

333
00:18:07,800 --> 00:18:09,880
with your figure and appearance,

334
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:11,590
even you are arrogant and incompetent,

335
00:18:11,590 --> 00:18:14,110
you can still live a smooth life?

336
00:18:14,110 --> 00:18:16,070
You don’t have to
lick the blood on the blade

337
00:18:16,070 --> 00:18:17,660
and wander around.

338
00:18:22,880 --> 00:18:24,590
Peerless talent

339
00:18:24,590 --> 00:18:26,590
and alluring beauty

340
00:18:26,590 --> 00:18:28,870
are rare in the world.

341
00:18:30,830 --> 00:18:31,460
However,

342
00:18:32,040 --> 00:18:34,040
if you grow into relying on it,

343
00:18:34,040 --> 00:18:35,710
it can easily become a cursed barrier

344
00:18:35,710 --> 00:18:37,590
that you can never get rid of.

345
00:18:39,190 --> 00:18:41,560
I was too arrogant

346
00:18:41,560 --> 00:18:43,190
and took myself too seriously,

347
00:18:43,190 --> 00:18:45,280
and I made a huge mistake.

348
00:18:46,640 --> 00:18:47,920
Drop all the nonsense.

349
00:18:47,920 --> 00:18:49,520
What do you want to say?

350
00:18:50,250 --> 00:18:50,930
Good.

351
00:18:51,760 --> 00:18:52,900
Remember,

352
00:18:53,280 --> 00:18:55,680
whoever says these things to you

353
00:18:55,680 --> 00:18:57,110
is harming you.

354
00:18:57,110 --> 00:18:58,800
Don’t believe a word.

355
00:19:00,470 --> 00:19:01,920
You must listen carefully

356
00:19:02,760 --> 00:19:04,160
about what I’m going to say.

357
00:19:06,190 --> 00:19:07,520
Please go ahead.

358
00:19:25,280 --> 00:19:28,400
Back then, the South and North Blades
were known to the world.

359
00:19:28,400 --> 00:19:29,640
The South Blade is extremely fierce.

360
00:19:29,640 --> 00:19:31,000
The North Blade is extremely dangerous.

361
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:33,070
It’s said that Water Cutting

362
00:19:33,070 --> 00:19:34,350
is for killing.

363
00:19:34,350 --> 00:19:35,710
But Snow-breaking Blade

364
00:19:35,710 --> 00:19:37,400
is the blade of master.

365
00:19:37,880 --> 00:19:39,680
Those who practice Snow-breaking Blade

366
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:41,450
are like walking alone on a snowy night.

367
00:19:41,880 --> 00:19:45,010
They must be extremely
strong and persistent

368
00:19:46,350 --> 00:19:48,520
to get a glimpse of it.

369
00:19:48,520 --> 00:19:52,650
Especially the three moves of
Invisible, Unpredictable and Edgeless.

370
00:19:52,950 --> 00:19:55,720
These moves seem to be unremarkable.

371
00:19:56,310 --> 00:19:58,710
But many people spend their whole life

372
00:19:58,710 --> 00:20:00,520
and still can’t master them.

373
00:20:03,040 --> 00:20:05,190
If you can’t master these three moves,

374
00:20:05,190 --> 00:20:06,880
no matter how great
your broadsword play is,

375
00:20:07,430 --> 00:20:08,950
no matter how powerful
your inner force is,

376
00:20:08,950 --> 00:20:10,530
the blade will still be soulless.

377
00:20:13,190 --> 00:20:14,430
Miss Zhou.

378
00:20:14,430 --> 00:20:15,560
I am worried

379
00:20:15,560 --> 00:20:17,040
that you might achieve nothing

380
00:20:18,800 --> 00:20:21,230
after you practiced it all these years.

381
00:20:21,230 --> 00:20:22,930
You said all these things

382
00:20:23,640 --> 00:20:25,300
just to curse me to achieve nothing?

383
00:20:28,710 --> 00:20:29,920
I’ve checked it out.

384
00:20:29,920 --> 00:20:32,680
Dragon Master left some people
to patrol the mountain.

385
00:20:32,680 --> 00:20:33,710
But there are just
a few people out there.

386
00:20:33,710 --> 00:20:35,190
Most of them went to the secret tunnel.

387
00:20:35,710 --> 00:20:37,400
Therefore, it’s safer to leave

388
00:20:37,400 --> 00:20:38,280
than to stay here.

389
00:20:38,280 --> 00:20:39,860
If we will get out,
we should leave now.

390
00:20:42,520 --> 00:20:43,590
Miss Zhou.

391
00:20:43,590 --> 00:20:46,800
Do you want to escape with them

392
00:20:48,710 --> 00:20:50,710
or stay here and take a risk

393
00:20:50,710 --> 00:20:51,830
to kill the Dragon Master

394
00:20:51,830 --> 00:20:53,590
with me?

395
00:21:03,070 --> 00:21:04,640
If you are willing to stay

396
00:21:04,640 --> 00:21:06,170
and kill the Dragon Master with me,

397
00:21:08,230 --> 00:21:10,950
I can teach you
the Water Cutting technique.

398
00:21:14,040 --> 00:21:16,110
You only need to stall
the Dragon Master for me.

399
00:21:16,110 --> 00:21:19,070
I’ll take care the rest of it.

400
00:21:19,070 --> 00:21:20,190
No way!

401
00:21:21,520 --> 00:21:22,950
You ask a little girl to

402
00:21:22,950 --> 00:21:25,000
resist one of the four lords
of Four-guardian Mountain?

403
00:21:32,520 --> 00:21:34,660
Unless you give her
an elixir of the Supreme Lord!

404
00:21:35,400 --> 00:21:36,640
Master Ji.

405
00:21:36,640 --> 00:21:38,070
I don’t want to be rude.

406
00:21:38,070 --> 00:21:40,160
It’s just everything is in the past.

407
00:21:40,680 --> 00:21:42,240
Why can’t you just bear it?

408
00:21:42,880 --> 00:21:43,880
Twenty years ago,

409
00:21:43,880 --> 00:21:45,520
you were stubborn.

410
00:21:45,520 --> 00:21:47,470
Now you are still that stubborn. You...!

411
00:21:47,470 --> 00:21:48,400
Fei.

412
00:21:48,400 --> 00:21:49,640
I don’t care about

413
00:21:49,640 --> 00:21:50,790
the life of that toy boy.

414
00:21:52,040 --> 00:21:54,040
You only need to
take care of Chuchu for me.

415
00:21:54,040 --> 00:21:54,860
You go first.

416
00:21:55,880 --> 00:21:56,480
You...!

417
00:22:05,280 --> 00:22:07,050
You said you knew how to deal with him.

418
00:22:07,710 --> 00:22:09,040
I can stay here to help you.

419
00:22:09,800 --> 00:22:11,680
But listen carefully to my words.

420
00:22:13,040 --> 00:22:14,310
I stay here

421
00:22:14,310 --> 00:22:16,400
to deal with that big mouse.

422
00:22:16,400 --> 00:22:17,470
As for the other things,

423
00:22:17,470 --> 00:22:18,800
you don’t need to teach me,

424
00:22:18,800 --> 00:22:20,400
and I won’t learn it.

425
00:22:20,400 --> 00:22:22,760
I won’t convert to other schools.

426
00:22:22,760 --> 00:22:24,920
South and North Blades are together.

427
00:22:24,920 --> 00:22:27,040
For the sake of my grandfather,

428
00:22:27,040 --> 00:22:28,570
I shouldn’t be disrespectful to you.

429
00:22:29,920 --> 00:22:32,710
But now I’ve met a senior like you,

430
00:22:32,710 --> 00:22:34,710
I must say something.

431
00:22:35,680 --> 00:22:38,520
Water Cutting is nothing.

432
00:22:42,760 --> 00:22:43,830
Yeah.

433
00:22:43,830 --> 00:22:45,430
Water Cutting

434
00:22:46,070 --> 00:22:47,680
is nothing.

435
00:22:51,350 --> 00:22:52,840
Anyway,

436
00:22:54,400 --> 00:22:55,800
thanks.

437
00:22:57,470 --> 00:22:59,360
Let’s go block the cave first.

438
00:23:19,230 --> 00:23:20,190
Did you find them?

439
00:23:20,190 --> 00:23:21,160
My lord.

440
00:23:21,160 --> 00:23:22,920
There is no obstruction in this passage.

441
00:23:22,920 --> 00:23:24,300
They should be at the deepest place.

442
00:23:25,160 --> 00:23:27,110
Good, keep going!

443
00:23:27,310 --> 00:23:28,210
Yes!

444
00:24:10,710 --> 00:24:12,160
Soul-searching Needle?

445
00:24:23,430 --> 00:24:25,040
What needle did you just say?

446
00:24:32,350 --> 00:24:33,710
Miss Zhou.

447
00:24:34,950 --> 00:24:36,430
To deal with Dragon Master,

448
00:24:36,430 --> 00:24:38,710
only my North Blade moves
can hold him at bay.

449
00:24:41,350 --> 00:24:43,650
Although I look like useless now,

450
00:24:44,040 --> 00:24:46,430
my previous power

451
00:24:46,430 --> 00:24:48,720
is enough to beat the Dragon Master.

452
00:24:55,190 --> 00:24:56,520
I’ll use this Soul-searching Needle

453
00:24:56,520 --> 00:24:58,310
to drive out my previous power.

454
00:24:58,310 --> 00:24:59,280
However,

455
00:24:59,950 --> 00:25:02,190
once I use the Soul-searching Needle,

456
00:25:02,190 --> 00:25:03,280
I need to close my eyes and rest.

457
00:25:03,280 --> 00:25:06,110
It takes quite a while to work.

458
00:25:06,110 --> 00:25:07,310
I need you to

459
00:25:07,310 --> 00:25:08,640
stall the Dragon Master for me

460
00:25:08,640 --> 00:25:10,630
until I get my power back.

461
00:25:17,760 --> 00:25:18,350
Okay.

462
00:25:19,760 --> 00:25:22,190
You looked down on my North Blade.

463
00:25:22,190 --> 00:25:24,350
Can I use Water Cutting

464
00:25:24,350 --> 00:25:26,190
to play against you?

465
00:25:26,190 --> 00:25:27,520
How?

466
00:25:27,520 --> 00:25:29,040
Sorry that I can’t fight.

467
00:25:29,040 --> 00:25:31,350
Miss Zhou, do you know
what verbal struggle is?

468
00:25:36,800 --> 00:25:39,000
Fighting is physical fighting.

469
00:25:39,000 --> 00:25:41,640
Verbal struggle is
exchanging techniques in meditation.

470
00:25:42,640 --> 00:25:43,880
In a verbal struggle,

471
00:25:43,880 --> 00:25:46,190
people only explain
the moves to each other,

472
00:25:46,190 --> 00:25:48,560
or just gesticulate

473
00:25:48,560 --> 00:25:49,800
without touching each other.

474
00:25:49,800 --> 00:25:50,830
No one will get hurt.

475
00:25:50,830 --> 00:25:52,070
It’s very peaceful.

476
00:25:54,310 --> 00:25:55,280
Miss Zhou.

477
00:25:57,070 --> 00:25:57,950
Please.

478
00:26:48,230 --> 00:26:49,070
Miss Zhou.

479
00:26:49,070 --> 00:26:51,760
Please make three moves of South Blade.

480
00:26:51,760 --> 00:26:53,830
I’ll respond with North Blade.

481
00:26:55,160 --> 00:26:55,900
Please.

482
00:27:16,110 --> 00:27:17,950
Why does Fei’s status

483
00:27:17,950 --> 00:27:19,800
change suddenly?

484
00:27:21,430 --> 00:27:23,000
That’s because

485
00:27:23,000 --> 00:27:24,710
Fei has been cut once

486
00:27:24,710 --> 00:27:26,190
by Water Cutting.

487
00:27:37,190 --> 00:27:38,400
The cover outside

488
00:27:38,400 --> 00:27:40,310
can only fool them for a while.

489
00:27:40,310 --> 00:27:41,040
In the end,

490
00:27:41,040 --> 00:27:43,590
I’m afraid I still need your help.

491
00:27:45,230 --> 00:27:47,270
It’s a narrow place here.

492
00:27:48,350 --> 00:27:50,280
No matter how many people they have,

493
00:27:50,280 --> 00:27:52,040
it’s hard for them to swarm up together.

494
00:27:52,040 --> 00:27:53,680
This is our advantage.

495
00:27:53,680 --> 00:27:56,590
The Dragon Master likes
bullying the weak the most.

496
00:27:57,310 --> 00:27:58,880
If he sees that you are a little girl,

497
00:27:58,880 --> 00:28:00,590
he will fight with you in person.

498
00:28:00,590 --> 00:28:03,230
His inner strength is far above you.

499
00:28:04,800 --> 00:28:06,280
What you can rely on

500
00:28:06,280 --> 00:28:08,160
is your peerless broadsword play.

501
00:28:08,160 --> 00:28:10,400
Next I will show you

502
00:28:10,400 --> 00:28:11,890
the peerless broadsword play.

503
00:28:12,520 --> 00:28:14,110
During tonight,

504
00:28:14,110 --> 00:28:15,950
if you can

505
00:28:15,950 --> 00:28:17,190
make twenty moves under my blade,

506
00:28:17,190 --> 00:28:19,470
the Dragon Master won’t be able to

507
00:28:19,470 --> 00:28:20,830
hurt you for a while.

508
00:28:20,830 --> 00:28:21,830
Let’s continue.

509
00:29:04,280 --> 00:29:04,880
My lord.

510
00:29:04,880 --> 00:29:06,230
The left tunnel is empty.

511
00:29:06,230 --> 00:29:08,070
My lord, the right tunnel is clear.

512
00:29:08,070 --> 00:29:09,390
Nothing on our end, my lord.

513
00:29:12,560 --> 00:29:13,160
Did they

514
00:29:13,160 --> 00:29:16,100
disappear into thin air?

515
00:29:21,880 --> 00:29:23,310
Get me All-listener.

516
00:29:23,310 --> 00:29:24,160
Yes.

517
00:29:35,400 --> 00:29:36,800
Why didn’t you strike?

518
00:29:42,950 --> 00:29:44,230
Unless your opponent

519
00:29:44,230 --> 00:29:46,000
is much weaker than you,

520
00:29:46,590 --> 00:29:48,760
either you’d let your weapon fly

521
00:29:48,760 --> 00:29:49,920
or get yourself hurt

522
00:29:49,920 --> 00:29:51,230
by that move.

523
00:29:52,760 --> 00:29:54,090
Is it that obvious even to you?

524
00:30:01,470 --> 00:30:02,330
Master Ji,

525
00:30:03,760 --> 00:30:05,330
I made a stupid remark.

526
00:30:06,280 --> 00:30:07,240
Please forgive me.

527
00:30:09,590 --> 00:30:10,260
Master Ji,

528
00:30:10,760 --> 00:30:12,070
how long

529
00:30:12,070 --> 00:30:13,090
will it take exactly?

530
00:30:14,040 --> 00:30:15,950
A few minutes,

531
00:30:15,950 --> 00:30:16,830
one hour,

532
00:30:16,830 --> 00:30:17,910
or two hours?

533
00:30:18,640 --> 00:30:19,760
If it’s two hours,

534
00:30:19,760 --> 00:30:21,590
I’d better go get coffins for us now.

535
00:30:21,590 --> 00:30:22,830
There might be good bargains.

536
00:30:22,830 --> 00:30:23,930
Knock it off!

537
00:30:24,920 --> 00:30:26,000
Go away.

538
00:30:27,710 --> 00:30:28,880
Mr. Xie,

539
00:30:28,880 --> 00:30:31,190
it’s hard to say.

540
00:30:31,190 --> 00:30:32,560
It could take minutes

541
00:30:32,560 --> 00:30:35,310
or hours.

542
00:30:37,350 --> 00:30:38,480
Mr. Xie,

543
00:30:38,830 --> 00:30:41,010
are you still trying to
change Fei’s mind?

544
00:30:43,280 --> 00:30:44,330
That girl’s patience

545
00:30:44,760 --> 00:30:46,500
is wearing thin.

546
00:30:46,880 --> 00:30:48,230
If I go on and on,

547
00:30:48,230 --> 00:30:50,400
she’ll be annoyed

548
00:30:50,400 --> 00:30:52,470
and kick me out of this world.

549
00:30:53,710 --> 00:30:56,000
Fei has a temper

550
00:30:56,000 --> 00:30:58,560
but I trust her the most.

551
00:30:58,560 --> 00:31:00,230
You’re being unfair to her.

552
00:31:03,280 --> 00:31:04,950
If the carrot doesn’t work,

553
00:31:04,950 --> 00:31:06,470
and I try the stick,

554
00:31:06,470 --> 00:31:08,350
the risk will be too high.

555
00:31:15,710 --> 00:31:16,310
Fei.

556
00:31:19,230 --> 00:31:21,680
Fei! Fei!

557
00:31:21,680 --> 00:31:23,280
I need to take Miss Wu away.

558
00:31:23,280 --> 00:31:24,800
This place is too dangerous to stay.

559
00:31:24,800 --> 00:31:26,160
She doesn’t listen to me.

560
00:31:26,160 --> 00:31:27,030
Why don’t you talk to her?

561
00:31:29,560 --> 00:31:30,470
Fei.

562
00:31:30,680 --> 00:31:31,920
I won’t leave.

563
00:31:31,920 --> 00:31:33,710
I’ll stay with you.

564
00:31:33,710 --> 00:31:34,830
Miss Wu,

565
00:31:34,830 --> 00:31:35,950
you’ve seen

566
00:31:35,950 --> 00:31:37,470
what Mu Xiaoqiao is capable of.

567
00:31:38,430 --> 00:31:39,880
I have.

568
00:31:39,880 --> 00:31:41,190
Dragon Master is as bad

569
00:31:41,190 --> 00:31:42,660
as him if not worse.

570
00:31:43,190 --> 00:31:43,990
So?

571
00:31:44,110 --> 00:31:46,430
As one of the Four Guardians,

572
00:31:46,430 --> 00:31:48,350
he’s highly skilled in martial arts

573
00:31:48,350 --> 00:31:50,680
and much crueler than you imagine.

574
00:31:50,680 --> 00:31:52,710
Once he tracks us down,

575
00:31:52,710 --> 00:31:53,880
all of us combined

576
00:31:53,880 --> 00:31:55,110
won’t be his match.

577
00:31:56,160 --> 00:31:57,070
What will happen

578
00:31:57,070 --> 00:31:58,590
if we fall into his hands?

579
00:31:58,590 --> 00:32:00,390
I’m not bluffing. Just think about it.

580
00:32:02,350 --> 00:32:03,040
Chuchu,

581
00:32:03,520 --> 00:32:04,760
leave with Xie Yun.

582
00:32:04,760 --> 00:32:06,800
Master Ji and I will stay.

583
00:32:13,760 --> 00:32:15,920
The rarest one owns

584
00:32:15,920 --> 00:32:17,950
isn’t unparalleled talent

585
00:32:19,040 --> 00:32:20,980
but a clear mind to know

586
00:32:22,400 --> 00:32:25,230
when to battle,

587
00:32:25,640 --> 00:32:28,200
when to take risks,

588
00:32:29,640 --> 00:32:31,930
when to be cautious

589
00:32:33,000 --> 00:32:35,590
and when to back off.

590
00:32:35,590 --> 00:32:37,310
One must know all that.

591
00:32:41,710 --> 00:32:42,990
Whose teaching is it

592
00:32:43,680 --> 00:32:44,890
that is

593
00:32:45,640 --> 00:32:47,680
to act against

594
00:32:47,680 --> 00:32:48,990
the situation?

595
00:32:50,230 --> 00:32:51,470
Hey,

596
00:32:52,350 --> 00:32:54,280
are you pointing the finger at me?

597
00:32:58,430 --> 00:32:59,920
I hope whoever I’m pointing at

598
00:33:00,400 --> 00:33:02,200
can understand me.

599
00:33:05,590 --> 00:33:06,520
Don’t you think I want to go home

600
00:33:06,520 --> 00:33:08,350
to practice my skills?

601
00:33:11,640 --> 00:33:12,680
But

602
00:33:12,680 --> 00:33:15,000
dictators like Dragon Master

603
00:33:15,000 --> 00:33:16,240
must be eliminated as soon as possible.

604
00:33:17,350 --> 00:33:19,470
Mr. Xie’s eyes are sharp.

605
00:33:19,470 --> 00:33:21,710
You must be well-versed
in all kinds of weapons.

606
00:33:21,710 --> 00:33:23,840
Are you specialized in the blade?

607
00:33:24,830 --> 00:33:25,880
You’re flattering me.

608
00:33:25,880 --> 00:33:27,640
If I’m specialized in anything,

609
00:33:27,640 --> 00:33:29,280
that’ll be escaping.

610
00:33:30,920 --> 00:33:33,040
The blade is single-edged

611
00:33:33,040 --> 00:33:34,710
while the sword is double-edged.

612
00:33:34,710 --> 00:33:36,920
A blade gives you courage

613
00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:39,190
because the edge

614
00:33:39,190 --> 00:33:40,310
is always in front of you.

615
00:33:41,230 --> 00:33:41,880
Correct.

616
00:33:41,880 --> 00:33:43,450
Just don’t hold it against your neck.

617
00:33:44,230 --> 00:33:46,210
Without such fighting spirit,

618
00:33:46,400 --> 00:33:47,980
however sharp

619
00:33:48,310 --> 00:33:49,360
the weapon is,

620
00:33:49,560 --> 00:33:51,150
it’s nothing but a heavy tool.

621
00:33:51,680 --> 00:33:53,860
Just learn from me.

622
00:33:54,310 --> 00:33:56,280
Snow-breaking Blade is powerful enough

623
00:33:56,280 --> 00:33:57,920
to break mountains and rivers.

624
00:33:57,920 --> 00:34:00,040
The enemy is close

625
00:34:00,040 --> 00:34:01,250
and she’s ready to kill him.

626
00:34:01,880 --> 00:34:03,590
If you talk her out of it,

627
00:34:03,590 --> 00:34:05,190
she’ll forever live in the shadow

628
00:34:05,190 --> 00:34:07,680
of weakness and cowardice.

629
00:34:08,120 --> 00:34:10,520
No matter how long she lives,

630
00:34:10,520 --> 00:34:13,280
she’ll only achieve so much

631
00:34:13,800 --> 00:34:15,460
as a blade user.

632
00:34:17,630 --> 00:34:18,390
Say no more.

633
00:34:23,630 --> 00:34:24,600
Relax.

634
00:34:24,600 --> 00:34:25,640
I won’t let you die.

635
00:34:28,150 --> 00:34:30,040
Were death is my concern,

636
00:34:30,040 --> 00:34:31,910
I’d be nowhere near you.

637
00:34:33,910 --> 00:34:36,390
Did...? Did I say anything wrong?

638
00:34:39,360 --> 00:34:41,430
I take you as my best friend

639
00:34:41,430 --> 00:34:42,840
yet you see me as some chicken.

640
00:34:58,320 --> 00:34:59,980
Master Ji’s Soul-searching Needle
is deadly.

641
00:35:00,630 --> 00:35:01,890
I’ll cover you.

642
00:35:10,040 --> 00:35:11,190
Uh...

643
00:35:13,000 --> 00:35:13,680
Thank you.

644
00:35:40,280 --> 00:35:42,950
I’m counting on you.

645
00:35:42,950 --> 00:35:45,120
Don’t let me down.

646
00:35:49,420 --> 00:35:51,740
(Wood)

647
00:35:57,080 --> 00:35:58,620
Gong Formation.

648
00:35:58,620 --> 00:36:00,700
(Wood)

649
00:36:10,230 --> 00:36:12,000
Miss Zhou, we’re running out of time.

650
00:36:12,000 --> 00:36:13,120
Let’s try again.

651
00:36:13,120 --> 00:36:14,470
Sure. One more time.

652
00:36:29,740 --> 00:36:31,700
(Water)

653
00:36:55,080 --> 00:36:57,870
Does Fei need help?

654
00:36:59,000 --> 00:37:00,520
Were Master Ji

655
00:37:00,520 --> 00:37:02,280
as skilled as before,

656
00:37:02,280 --> 00:37:03,230
Fei

657
00:37:03,230 --> 00:37:04,950
would stand a chance to fight back.

658
00:37:05,560 --> 00:37:06,360
Why?

659
00:37:06,360 --> 00:37:08,760
She practices various skills

660
00:37:08,760 --> 00:37:11,120
and she can think outside the box

661
00:37:11,120 --> 00:37:12,700
when fighting against others.

662
00:37:13,040 --> 00:37:14,000
The Mayfly Formation

663
00:37:14,000 --> 00:37:15,300
she learned from that Taoist priest

664
00:37:15,760 --> 00:37:17,470
has added even more diversity

665
00:37:17,470 --> 00:37:19,120
to her style.

666
00:37:19,560 --> 00:37:21,560
Even Dragon Master

667
00:37:21,560 --> 00:37:23,190
can’t kill her at once.

668
00:37:23,190 --> 00:37:24,760
But the thing is

669
00:37:24,760 --> 00:37:25,950
she and Master Ji

670
00:37:25,950 --> 00:37:28,080
aren’t engaging in actual combat.

671
00:37:28,080 --> 00:37:30,120
How is that

672
00:37:30,120 --> 00:37:31,630
a problem?

673
00:37:33,870 --> 00:37:34,870
In the eyes of the outsiders,

674
00:37:35,190 --> 00:37:36,760
meditation

675
00:37:36,760 --> 00:37:39,000
is bland and boring.

676
00:37:39,560 --> 00:37:40,520
But that’s because you don’t understand

677
00:37:40,520 --> 00:37:42,280
what they’re doing

678
00:37:42,280 --> 00:37:44,120
and how demanding

679
00:37:44,120 --> 00:37:45,430
it is.

680
00:37:45,430 --> 00:37:46,800
In a fight,

681
00:37:46,800 --> 00:37:48,470
agility, strength,

682
00:37:48,470 --> 00:37:49,670
skills

683
00:37:49,670 --> 00:37:50,950
and even the mental state

684
00:37:50,950 --> 00:37:52,360
may affect the result.

685
00:37:52,360 --> 00:37:54,230
Are you saying

686
00:37:54,230 --> 00:37:56,520
Fei is restricted

687
00:37:56,520 --> 00:37:58,870
in meditation?

688
00:37:58,870 --> 00:37:59,840
Yes.

689
00:38:00,670 --> 00:38:03,060
While Master Ji sits there,

690
00:38:03,630 --> 00:38:04,560
Fei

691
00:38:04,560 --> 00:38:06,710
can’t jump around him.

692
00:38:06,710 --> 00:38:08,910
Forget about the Mayfly Formation

693
00:38:08,910 --> 00:38:10,840
or other

694
00:38:10,840 --> 00:38:12,520
gimmicks or tricks

695
00:38:12,520 --> 00:38:14,030
to battle against Water Cutting,

696
00:38:14,710 --> 00:38:16,040
her only choice is to strike

697
00:38:16,040 --> 00:38:17,520
with the Snow-breaking Blade

698
00:38:17,520 --> 00:38:18,690
one by one.

699
00:38:20,710 --> 00:38:22,280
That’s

700
00:38:22,280 --> 00:38:24,010
difficult for Fei.

701
00:38:24,470 --> 00:38:27,280
Although Master Ji lost his skills,

702
00:38:27,280 --> 00:38:29,080
he was the North Blade.

703
00:38:29,080 --> 00:38:30,430
Every move

704
00:38:30,430 --> 00:38:32,080
is destructive,

705
00:38:35,320 --> 00:38:36,710
and can easily

706
00:38:36,710 --> 00:38:39,190
trap others into his invisible attacks.

707
00:38:41,950 --> 00:38:44,320
I wonder if Fei can succeed

708
00:38:44,320 --> 00:38:46,280
within such a short time.

709
00:38:47,000 --> 00:38:49,230
Has she ever failed us?

710
00:39:07,360 --> 00:39:08,800
My lord.

711
00:39:08,800 --> 00:39:10,360
I’ve located them.

712
00:39:25,120 --> 00:39:26,040
Fei.

713
00:39:29,120 --> 00:39:30,560
Do you need some rest?

714
00:39:31,950 --> 00:39:34,230
Miss Zhou, you successfully

715
00:39:34,230 --> 00:39:36,560
took five strikes.

716
00:39:38,470 --> 00:39:39,320
Just now,

717
00:39:40,000 --> 00:39:42,090
when the blades touched,

718
00:39:42,870 --> 00:39:45,100
I got hold of the gist
of the Mountain Move.

719
00:39:46,150 --> 00:39:48,300
That is to shake hardness with thinness,

720
00:39:48,950 --> 00:39:51,630
to break heaviness with tininess.

721
00:39:52,520 --> 00:39:53,280
I learned

722
00:39:53,280 --> 00:39:55,190
that very first move

723
00:39:55,190 --> 00:39:57,390
a long time ago,

724
00:39:57,390 --> 00:39:58,670
but

725
00:39:59,360 --> 00:40:02,190
I didn’t truly understand it

726
00:40:02,190 --> 00:40:04,950
until being inspired by you.

727
00:40:07,000 --> 00:40:08,320
Well done!

728
00:40:09,360 --> 00:40:10,630
You’ve managed

729
00:40:10,630 --> 00:40:12,470
to have such an epiphany so quickly.

730
00:40:12,470 --> 00:40:13,630
No wonder you’re a heroine.

731
00:40:13,630 --> 00:40:15,710
You’re one of a kind,

732
00:40:15,710 --> 00:40:17,120
a real talent.

733
00:40:18,840 --> 00:40:19,840
And

734
00:40:20,710 --> 00:40:22,300
I was thinking

735
00:40:23,600 --> 00:40:26,300
the nine moves are
often used separately.

736
00:40:27,390 --> 00:40:28,950
Is it possible

737
00:40:28,950 --> 00:40:31,910
to combine those two moves?

738
00:40:33,430 --> 00:40:34,600
As far as I know,

739
00:40:34,600 --> 00:40:35,630
with a single blade,

740
00:40:35,630 --> 00:40:37,890
you can only strike left or right.

741
00:40:38,430 --> 00:40:39,870
Combining the moves

742
00:40:39,870 --> 00:40:41,180
is impractical.

743
00:40:41,950 --> 00:40:43,230
Only

744
00:40:43,230 --> 00:40:44,840
a thorough master

745
00:40:44,840 --> 00:40:46,020
can improve the skills.

746
00:40:46,950 --> 00:40:48,430
With that being said,

747
00:40:49,800 --> 00:40:51,520
every time

748
00:40:51,520 --> 00:40:53,890
I changed my moves,

749
00:40:54,670 --> 00:40:56,430
I felt as if my Yellow and Green Spirit

750
00:40:56,430 --> 00:40:59,200
had guided me

751
00:41:00,280 --> 00:41:01,470
to better understand the blade.

752
00:41:03,520 --> 00:41:05,100
Old Master Li’s blade

753
00:41:05,950 --> 00:41:07,600
is edgeless

754
00:41:07,600 --> 00:41:09,360
while Leader Li’s

755
00:41:09,360 --> 00:41:10,800
is invisible.

756
00:41:10,800 --> 00:41:12,000
Miss,

757
00:41:12,390 --> 00:41:13,760
what about yours?

758
00:41:15,080 --> 00:41:16,840
The blade doesn’t define us

759
00:41:16,840 --> 00:41:18,360
but we define the blade.

760
00:41:18,630 --> 00:41:20,150
The North Blade is like water.

761
00:41:20,150 --> 00:41:21,470
Blade can’t cut off water for real,

762
00:41:21,470 --> 00:41:23,120
so why bother

763
00:41:23,120 --> 00:41:25,430
to invest in so much strength

764
00:41:26,080 --> 00:41:28,360
but only to get weakened

765
00:41:28,360 --> 00:41:30,640
and neutralized?

766
00:41:33,000 --> 00:41:34,320
My blade should be unpredictable.

767
00:41:39,040 --> 00:41:40,950
Your grandfather would be proud

768
00:41:40,950 --> 00:41:42,000
to have such

769
00:41:42,000 --> 00:41:43,800
an insightful and talented

770
00:41:43,800 --> 00:41:44,840
heiress.

771
00:41:45,800 --> 00:41:48,560
Dragon Master might be here any minute.

772
00:41:48,560 --> 00:41:50,810
Let’s waste no time.

773
00:41:51,870 --> 00:41:52,430
Sure.

774
00:42:36,280 --> 00:42:37,470
I don’t know what others

775
00:42:37,470 --> 00:42:38,840
practice martial arts for.

776
00:42:38,840 --> 00:42:39,430
Maybe some

777
00:42:39,430 --> 00:42:41,560
are eager to establish their own sects

778
00:42:41,560 --> 00:42:43,840
while others

779
00:42:43,840 --> 00:42:46,330
always fight to be number one.

780
00:42:47,190 --> 00:42:48,400
But Fei is different.

781
00:42:52,120 --> 00:42:54,800
She has a strong interest in the skills

782
00:42:54,800 --> 00:42:56,560
but can’t care less

783
00:42:56,560 --> 00:42:57,950
about the title.

784
00:42:59,040 --> 00:43:00,320
I agree.

785
00:43:00,320 --> 00:43:02,760
She’s competitive

786
00:43:02,760 --> 00:43:04,280
but she isn’t obsessed

787
00:43:04,280 --> 00:43:05,910
with winning.

788
00:43:06,670 --> 00:43:08,190
Actually,

789
00:43:08,190 --> 00:43:10,040
she reminds me of Mr. Wuliu

790
00:43:11,040 --> 00:43:12,020
who always forgets to eat

791
00:43:12,710 --> 00:43:13,950
whenever he discovers something new.

792
00:43:15,840 --> 00:43:17,320
Mr. Xie,

793
00:43:17,320 --> 00:43:18,670
you know Fei too well.

794
00:43:38,120 --> 00:43:38,980
Oh, no!

795
00:43:40,760 --> 00:43:42,630
Listen.

796
00:43:42,630 --> 00:43:44,840
They’re getting closer to us.

797
00:43:44,840 --> 00:43:45,840
Calm down.

798
00:43:45,840 --> 00:43:47,170
They might not find this place.

799
00:43:51,760 --> 00:43:53,230
How long

800
00:43:53,230 --> 00:43:54,630
will they still need?

801
00:43:54,630 --> 00:43:56,040
Given her talent,

802
00:43:56,040 --> 00:43:57,430
it won’t be too long,

803
00:43:57,430 --> 00:43:58,470
but the loud noise

804
00:43:58,470 --> 00:44:00,520
we hear

805
00:44:00,520 --> 00:44:02,290
may distract her.

806
00:44:02,950 --> 00:44:05,050
I wonder if she can still focus.

807
00:45:28,150 --> 00:45:29,540
They seem to have left.

808
00:45:30,390 --> 00:45:32,190
That fake alley

809
00:45:32,190 --> 00:45:33,470
must’ve tricked them.

810
00:45:34,150 --> 00:45:35,190
I suppose.

811
00:45:35,190 --> 00:45:36,640
But they’ll find out sooner or later.

812
00:45:37,710 --> 00:45:39,040
Not too soon, I hope.

813
00:45:49,010 --> 00:45:52,520
♪Stars flow like river♪

814
00:45:53,580 --> 00:45:57,180
♪My yearning falls into the river♪

815
00:45:57,750 --> 00:46:01,820
♪Now that you’re in my life♪

816
00:46:02,070 --> 00:46:05,710
♪I will never be alone♪

817
00:46:05,710 --> 00:46:09,830
♪I haven’t seen the mountains with you♪

818
00:46:10,250 --> 00:46:14,680
♪Nor have I tied up your hair♪

819
00:46:15,340 --> 00:46:19,900
♪We haven’t finished our story in chaos♪

820
00:46:20,130 --> 00:46:24,760
♪The blade hasn’t been returned♪

821
00:46:24,950 --> 00:46:28,780
♪I fear not to roam the world with you♪

822
00:46:29,000 --> 00:46:33,690
♪When I go across the world for you♪

823
00:46:33,950 --> 00:46:37,690
♪I’m willing to shed blood for you♪

824
00:46:38,020 --> 00:46:43,110
♪Don’t mind whose land it is♪

825
00:46:43,110 --> 00:46:47,050
♪Where is home to the snowflake♪

826
00:46:47,050 --> 00:46:51,580
♪Come and melt in my embrace♪

827
00:46:52,200 --> 00:46:59,300
♪The spring sun is an invisible armor
that’ll hold♪

828
00:47:00,040 --> 00:47:04,670
♪The purest love is unadorned♪
